mistral.reason: Scarface: The World Is Yours is not strictly an open-world movie, but rather an open-world action game based on the movie Scarface.

gemma2.reason: It describes a game as an open-world movie, which is a contradiction. Movies are a visual medium while video games are interactive experiences with player agency.

llama3.1.reason: Scarface: The World Is Yours is an open-world action-adventure video game, not a movie.

qwen2.5.reason: Scarface: The World Is Yours is described as an open-world action game, not a movie. It contains gameplay elements reminiscent of the Grand Theft Auto series and has features such as a notoriety system, which are inconsistent with it being solely a movie adaptation.
